{
  "texts": [
    "In the Evidence Retrieval experiment, BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5 outperformed all-mpnet-base-v2 by 1.06% on F1@1 and 1.32% on F1@10, both statistically significant at the 5% level.",
    "dunzhang/stella_en_1.5B_v5 showed an average improvement of 7.44% over BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5 across all F1 values.",
    "This result was statistically significant with p = 1.59 × 10 -5, highlighting the critical role of embedding models in retrieval tasks.",
    "See Tables 21 22 23 for full F1 scores from the three embedding models on evidence retrieval.",
    "For Figures 2 3 4 5, all scores are normalized and averaged across datasets and k values."
  ]
}